4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a novel concept for bundle-specific tractography based on a learned mapping from the original fiber orientation distribution function (fODF) peaks to a list of tract orientation maps (TOMs), which involves artificial intelligence techniques.
